      "side": 1,
      "message": "By this, you mean the PT_DYNAMIC segment, right? Can you call it out by name here?\n\nIn fact, maybe you should call this whole class (and its filename) ElfDynamicSegmentReader to make that even clearer.",
      "revId": "ee519d37bcefddd4852adf8bf9f0cde9c1a4b551",
