        "filename": "util/linux/elf_image_reader.cc",
        "patchSetId": 19
      },
      "lineNbr": 47,
      "author": {
        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-06-23T21:42:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think it makes more sense to expose GetPreferredBaseAddress() here, and leave the computation of the load bias to ElfImageReader::Initialize(). There’s no reason to have to push the concept of “actual” into an object of this class.",
      "revId": "ee519d37bcefddd4852adf8bf9f0cde9c1a4b551",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
