        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-06-23T21:42:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Capitalize GNU.\n\nAnd PT_DYNAMIC is a segment, not a section, so say section.\n\nAnd “linker” is confusing terminology, can you refer to it as “loader” here and on the next line?",
      "revId": "ee519d37bcefddd4852adf8bf9f0cde9c1a4b551",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
