    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "2c919c74_a3008a17",
        "filename": "util/linux/elf_image_reader.cc",
        "patchSetId": 19
      },
      "lineNbr": 198,
      "author": {
        "id": 1174099
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-06-23T21:42:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Verify fields that you can deal with here. At the very least, e_version should be EV_CURRENT.\n\nI also think that you should verify e_type, because not all ELF files are loaded modules. ET_EXEC and ET_DYN are, but if someone’s mapped a core file (ET_CORE) or an object file (ET_REL), we wouldn’t want to mess with it here.",
      "revId": "ee519d37bcefddd4852adf8bf9f0cde9c1a4b551",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
